slack and chrome need "--force-device-scale-factor" to look normally. 
add it to /usr/bin/chrome and /usr/local/applications/slack

remember about .gitconfig.local, which isn't in .dotfiles repo

copy etc/systemd/system files to /etc/systemd/system (as root), then systemctl enable them

copy etc/udev/rules.d/10-trackpoint.rules to /etc/udev/rules.d/10-trackpoint.rules  
